{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Cond\/waitUntil(mutex:endTime:)"},"abstract":[{"text":"Waits until either ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"cond"},{"text":" is signalled or ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"endTime"},{"type":"text","text":" has passed."}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Cond","doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Cond\/CondProtocol-Implementations"]]},"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/glib\/cond\/waituntil(mutex:endtime:)"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"waitUntil","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"kind":"genericParameter","text":"MutexT"},{"kind":"text","text":">("},{"text":"mutex","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"MutexT","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"endTime"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@gint64","text":"gint64"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Bool","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"where","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"MutexT"},{"kind":"text","text":" : "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:4GLib13MutexProtocolP","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/MutexProtocol","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"MutexProtocol"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"As with "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_cond_wait()"},{"type":"text","text":" it is possible that a spurious or stolen wakeup"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"could occur.  For that reason, waiting on a condition variable should","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"always be in a loop, based on an explicitly-checked predicate."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"code":"true","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is returned if the condition variable was signalled (or in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"case of a spurious wakeup).  "},{"code":"false","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is returned if "},{"code":"endTime","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" has","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"passed."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The following code shows how to correctly perform a timed wait on a"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"condition variable (extending the example presented in the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"documentation for ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Cond"},{"text":"):","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"(C Language Example):","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"C","type":"codeListing","code":["gpointer","pop_data_timed (void)","{","  gint64 end_time;","  gpointer data;","","  g_mutex_lock (&data_mutex);","","  end_time = g_get_monotonic_time () + 5 * G_TIME_SPAN_SECOND;","  while (!current_data)","    if (!g_cond_wait_until (&data_cond, &data_mutex, end_time))","      {","        \/\/ timeout has passed.","        g_mutex_unlock (&data_mutex);","        return NULL;","      }","","  \/\/ there is data for us","  data = current_data;","  current_data = NULL;","","  g_mutex_unlock (&data_mutex);","","  return data;","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Notice that the end time is calculated once, before entering the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"loop and reused.  This is the motivation behind the use of absolute"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"time on this API – if a relative time of 5 seconds were passed"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"directly to the call and a spurious wakeup occurred, the program would","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"have to start over waiting again (which would lead to a total wait","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"time of more than 5 seconds).","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"waitUntil"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"text":"MutexT","kind":"genericParameter"},{"text":">(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"mutex"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"MutexT","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"text":"endTime","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@gint64","text":"gint64","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Bool"}],"symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"GLib"}],"extendedModule":"GLib","roleHeading":"Instance Method","externalID":"s:4GLib12CondProtocolPAAE9waitUntil5mutex7endTimeSbqd___s5Int64VtAA05MutexC0Rd__lF::SYNTHESIZED::s:4GLib4CondC","title":"waitUntil(mutex:endTime:)"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"references":{"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib":{"abstract":[],"kind":"symbol","title":"GLib","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/glib","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","type":"topic"},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/Cond/CondProtocol-Implementations":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Cond\/CondProtocol-Implementations","type":"topic","abstract":[],"title":"CondProtocol Implementations","url":"\/documentation\/glib\/cond\/condprotocol-implementations","kind":"article","role":"collectionGroup"},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/Cond/waitUntil(mutex:endTime:)":{"abs